---
const stats = [
  { value: '+106', label: 'Clientes ativos que crescem com a Lookall', color: 'blue' },
  { value: '83',   label: 'Projetos digitais entregues com sucesso', color: 'green' },
];
---

<section
  id="resultados"
  class="bg-white py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"
  aria-labelledby="stats-heading"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Top: two-column -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-14">
      <div>
        <span class="text-sm font-bold text-[#f5c518] uppercase tracking-widest">Nossos Números</span>
        <h2
          id="stats-heading"
          class="mt-3 text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-[#0b0f1a] leading-tight"
        >
          Números que <span class="italic text-[#2e5bff]">fazem a caixa</span> da<br />
          sua empresa girar.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-5">
        <p class="text-lg text-[#5b6473] leading-relaxed">
          Mais de uma centena de empresas já transformaram seu crescimento digital com a Lookall. Cada número representa uma história de sucesso real.
        </p>
        <a
          href="#contato"
          class="self-start inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-[#0b0f1a] text-white font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-[#1a2130] transition-colors"
        >
          Quero esses resultados
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats: 2 large cards -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-2xl">
      {stats.map((stat) => (
        <div class={`group p-8 rounded-2xl border transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg ${stat.color === 'blue' ? 'border-[#2e5bff]/20 bg-[#2e5bff]/5 hover:border-[#2e5bff]/40' : 'border-[#1fbf6b]/20 bg-[#1fbf6b]/5 hover:border-[#1fbf6b]/40'}`}>
          <p class={`text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-black mb-3 ${stat.color === 'blue' ? 'text-[#2e5bff]' : 'text-[#1fbf6b]'}`}>
            {stat.value}
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-[#374151] leading-snug">{stat.label}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
